<tr>
<td>Mandat</td>
<td>Mandat</td>
<td>Director authorization status</td>
<td>&quot;Not reviewed&quot;</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</li>
<li><p>Invoice lines from mandats that have been authorized for payment by the director, but not yet approved by the accountant.</p>
<table>
